
Install terraform 

   https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/install

Install aws cli

1.aws configure

2.enter access key and secret key

set the path in environment variables

create a main.tf file in the terraform path

Now open the cmd with the destination path

## Follow the commands to run the terraform script on cmd

1. terraform init

2.terraform plan

3.terraform apply

By following these commands it will run the script then the ec2 instance will be created in the aws console.
